Anyone who've encountered Japanese in business meetings will know 1/ You better carry enough business cards with you 2/ When you receive the card from another person or when you give yours, make sure using both hands. And bend your body a little. And nod when reading the name. 3/ Never ever put the card in your pocket right away if you're gonna have a table meeting with more than one person.
